      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "面对一个庞大又棘手的问题，我们常常无从下手。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.92,
      "size": 30672,
      "text": "分治的思路是：把大问题一分为二，再各个击破。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "就像整理一副乱牌，先分成两小堆，分别理好，再合到一起。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "div-1",
      "filename": "divide-div-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/divide-div-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "第一步是分解，把数组从中间切开，得到左右两半。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "divide",
      "line_id": "div-2",
      "filename": "divide-div-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/divide-div-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.0,
      "size": 31968,
      "text": "每一半继续二分，一层层向下，直到只剩单个元素。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "conquer",
      "line_id": "con-2",
      "filename": "conquer-con-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/conquer-con-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.8,
      "size": 28800,
      "text": "递归树的每个分叉，都是一个规模更小的相同问题。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "mer-1",
      "filename": "merge-mer-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/merge-mer-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.48,
      "size": 39744,
      "text": "子问题解好后，关键一步是合并：把两个有序小段拼成一个有序大段。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "divide-conquer",
      "section_id": "merge",
      "line_id": "mer-2",
      "filename": "merge-mer-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/divide-conquer/yunxi/merge-mer-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.15,
      "size": 34416,
      "text": "两个指针各指一段头部，每次取较小的放入结果，逐步归并。"
    }
